{"tid":2093700,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發：特朗普長子個女友中左武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-07-04T04:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T16:26:37.000Z","uid":324930,"like":138,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"761b4753c0e35d8fb08eff6c798ece8cfb744fd1","tid":2093700,"uid":324930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"美國傳媒報道，總統特朗普長子唐納德的女友、前霍士新聞女主播吉爾福伊爾（Kimberly Guilfoyle），周五（3日）確診新冠肺炎，屬無徵狀感染。消息指，唐納德沒有染疫，二人將乘車回家，不會坐飛機。<br />\n據報，51歲的吉爾福伊爾原定周五晚出席南達科他州拉什莫爾山的活動。特朗普當晚在拉什莫爾山有演說，她與唐納德都沒有與特朗普接觸，亦沒有與特朗普同乘空軍一號到當地。<br />\n吉爾福伊爾與42歲的唐納德於2018年開始約會，她是加州民主黨籍州長紐瑟姆的前妻。她曾是霍士新聞主播，目前是特朗普競選團隊的成員，是特朗普勝利財務委員會主席，專責競選經費籌集工作，時常與唐納德一同出席籌款活動。<br />\n<br />\n汁：東方唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cSVPPOHCOLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcSVPPOHCOLc&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=203ee678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cSVPPOHCOLc</a>"},{"pid":"7441ec74f8130b21b9b7d6b5ccfdb79bada5e46e","tid":2093700,"uid":1971,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:46:09.000Z","msg":"China!!!!"},{"pid":"97c1bb7f9b427fbb719382fc8673e0119ae1f1ad","tid":2093700,"uid":172627,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"長子病危會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fb23df4403b7e3fe11b0a5ed883d22b6addedc","tid":2093700,"uid":241504,"like":15,"dislike":215,"score":-200,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"快啲死全家"},{"pid":"278e81333237b6c43c020a546ace1e0851f240bf","tid":2093700,"uid":114217,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:29:22.000Z","msg":"侵仔叫爸爸出手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87aa02982af327e480ae64ebe918f7f2eb7b49ac","tid":2093700,"uid":248290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0